<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Veja como vai ficar seu projeto</title>

  <style>
    /*
      =========================================================
      VISUALIZADOR PROFISSIONAL PARA DESIGNERS — INDEX.HTML
      ---------------------------------------------------------
      Arquitetura pensada para produtos gráficos reais.

      PRODUTOS:
      1. Livro (2 a 16 paginas)
      2. Livreto / Folder
         - 1 dobra:  bi-fold (4 pgs)
         - 2 dobras: rollfold, zfold, gatefold (6 pgs)
         - 3 dobras: rollfold, zfold, paralela dupla (8 pgs)
         - 4 dobras: rollfold, zfold (10 pgs)
      3. Frente e verso
      4. Embalagem 3D

      PONTOS IMPORTANTES:
      - Separa lógica de leitura e lógica física.
      - Folder usa mapeamento de imposição.
      - Roll-fold tem compensação de aba interna.
      - Embalagem 3D usa width, height e depth reais.
      - Upload em massa distribui imagens na ordem lógica.
      - Modo técnico mostra pranchetas externa/interna.
      =========================================================
    */

    :root {
      --bg-1: #070914;
      --bg-2: #111827;
      --panel: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
      --panel-strong: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      --dark-glass: rgba(3, 7, 18, 0.62);
      --stroke: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      --stroke-strong: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.24);
      --text: #f8fbff;
      --muted: rgba(248, 251, 255, 0.66);
      --muted-2: rgba(248, 251, 255, 0.46);
      --paper: #fffaf0;
      --paper-2: #f1eadb;
      --accent: #06b6c7;
      --accent-2: #8b5cf6;
      --success: #34d399;
      --warning: #fbbf24;
      --danger: #fb7185;
      --radius-xl: 30px;
      --radius-lg: 22px;
      --radius-md: 14px;
      --ease: cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
      --page-w: 1;
      --page-h: 1.414;
      --cols: 1;
      --doc-width: 860px;
      --gap: 0px;
      --box-w: 320px;
      --box-h: 440px;
      --box-d: 140px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    html, body {
      margin: 0;
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 100%;
      color: var(--text);
      background: var(--bg-1);
      font-family: Inter, Roboto, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 15% 12%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.26), transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 84% 16%, rgba(6, 182, 199, 0.22), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 100%, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.14), transparent 36%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-1), var(--bg-2));
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.034) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.034) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 44px 44px;
      mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black, transparent 72%);
      opacity: 0.55;
    }

    button, input, select { font: inherit; }

    .app {
      position: relative;
      width: min(1660px, 100%);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .shell {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) 430px;
      gap: 24px;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 56px);
    }

    .main {
      min-width: 0;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: auto minmax(560px, 1fr) auto;
      gap: 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.075), rgba(255,255,255,0.035));
      box-shadow: 0 24px 90px rgba(0,0,0,0.27);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 26px 28px 0;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      width: fit-content;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--stroke);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.075);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }

    .eyebrow::before {
      content: "";
      width: 7px;
      height: 7px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(6,182,199,0.72);
    }

    h1 {
      max-width: 820px;
      margin: 16px 0 10px;
      font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 72px);
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -0.07em;
    }

    .subtitle {
      max-width: 820px;
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: clamp(14px, 1.4vw, 17px);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .project-summary {
      min-width: 265px;
      align-self: start;
      padding: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--stroke);
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.075);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    }

    .summary-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      padding: 8px 0;
    }

    .summary-row + .summary-row { border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
    .summary-row strong { color: var(--text); text-align: right; font-weight: 900; }

    .stage-wrap {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 560px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr auto;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 26px 28px;
      overflow: auto;
    }

    .stage-bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 26px;
      border-radius: 32px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 18%, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), transparent 30%),
        rgba(4, 8, 18, 0.28);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .viewer {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 520px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      perspective: 1900px;
      overflow: visible;
    }

    .viewer::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      bottom: 7%;
      width: min(82%, 980px);
      height: 68px;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(0,0,0,0.48), transparent 66%);
      filter: blur(18px);
      opacity: 0.84;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .caption {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 3;
      width: min(100%, 980px);
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    .flat-doc {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 3;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(var(--cols), minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: var(--gap);
      width: min(100%, var(--doc-width));
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 28px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.32));
      animation: flatIn 680ms var(--ease) both;
    }

    @keyframes flatIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px) scale(0.96); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
    }

    .page, .panel-page {
      position: relative;
      aspect-ratio: var(--page-w) / var(--page-h);
      min-width: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--paper);
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.08),
        0 10px 22px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
    }

    .flat-doc:not(.has-gap) .page:not(:first-child),
    .flat-doc:not(.has-gap) .panel-page:not(:first-child) {
      border-left: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
    }

    .round-left { border-top-left-radius: 10px; border-bottom-left-radius: 10px; }
    .round-right { border-top-right-radius: 10px; border-bottom-right-radius: 10px; }

    .page::after, .panel-page::after, .box-face::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 5;
      pointer-events: none;
      background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.08), transparent 8%, transparent 92%, rgba(0,0,0,0.07)),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.22), transparent 48%);
      mix-blend-mode: multiply;
      opacity: 0.72;
    }

    .page-media, .placeholder {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .page-media {
      z-index: 2;
      object-fit: cover;
      opacity: 1;
      transition: opacity 220ms ease;
    }

    .placeholder {
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 18px;
      color: rgba(0,0,0,0.52);
      text-align: center;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 30% 18%, rgba(6,182,199,0.12), transparent 25%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #fffaf0, #e9e1d1);
    }

    .placeholder-inner { display: grid; justify-items: center; gap: 10px; }
    .placeholder-icon {
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }
    .placeholder-inner span { max-width: 180px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.35; font-weight: 800; }

    .page-title {
      position: absolute;
      z-index: 8;
      left: 50%;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      color: rgba(0,0,0,0.46);
      font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 58px);
      line-height: 1;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: -0.065em;
      white-space: nowrap;
      pointer-events: none;
      text-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      transition: opacity 200ms ease;
    }

    .page-badge {
      position: absolute;
      z-index: 9;
      left: 12px;
      top: 12px;
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.68);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      transition: opacity 200ms ease;
    }

    .panel-mm {
      position: absolute;
      z-index: 10;
      right: 10px;
      bottom: 10px;
      padding: 6px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.86);
      color: rgba(15,23,42,0.72);
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 950;
    }

    .hide-titles .page-title,
    .hide-titles .page-badge,
    .hide-titles .panel-mm,
    .presentation .page-title,
    .presentation .page-badge,
    .presentation .panel-mm { opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; }
    .hide-images .page-media { opacity: 0; }

    .opening-doc {
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
      transform: rotateX(0deg) rotateY(-4deg);
    }
    .opening-doc .page:nth-child(1) { transform-origin: right center; animation: leftPageOpen 780ms var(--ease) both; }
    .opening-doc .page:nth-child(2) { transform-origin: left center; animation: rightPageOpen 780ms var(--ease) both; }
    @keyframes leftPageOpen { from { transform: rotateY(64deg); filter: brightness(0.74); } to { transform: rotateY(0deg); filter: brightness(1); } }
    @keyframes rightPageOpen { from { transform: rotateY(-64deg); filter: brightness(0.74); } to { transform: rotateY(0deg); filter: brightness(1); } }

    /* ========= ANIMACOES DE DOBRA POR MODO ========= */
    .fold-opening { transform-style: preserve-3d; perspective: 1800px; }
    .fold-opening .page {
      animation: foldPanelIn 620ms var(--ease) both;
      animation-delay: calc(var(--panel-index, 0) * 130ms);
      transform-origin: var(--panel-origin, left center);
    }
    @keyframes foldPanelIn {
      from {
        transform: rotateY(var(--panel-from, -110deg));
        opacity: 0.35;
        filter: brightness(0.72);
      }
      to {
        transform: rotateY(0deg);
        opacity: 1;
        filter: brightness(1);
      }
    }

    .fold-opening.mode-book {
      transform: rotateX(0deg) rotateY(-3deg);
    }

    .fold-opening.mode-roll {
      transform: rotateX(0deg) rotateY(-6deg);
    }

    .fold-opening.mode-z {
      transform: rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg);
    }

    .fold-opening.mode-gate {
      transform: rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg);
    }

    .fold-opening.mode-parallel {
      transform: rotateX(0deg) rotateY(-5deg);
    }

    /* Animacao do Verso (girada 180) */
    .fold-back-flip {
      animation: foldBackFlip 760ms var(--ease) both;
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
    }
    @keyframes foldBackFlip {
      0%   { transform: rotateY(0deg) scale(1); opacity: 1; filter: brightness(1); }
      45%  { transform: rotateY(90deg) scale(0.96); opacity: 0.55; filter: brightness(0.7); }
      55%  { transform: rotateY(-90deg) scale(0.96); opacity: 0.55; filter: brightness(0.7); }
      100% { transform: rotateY(0deg) scale(1); opacity: 1; filter: brightness(1); }
    }

    /* Botoes especiais do Folder */
    .btn.btn-action {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    }
    .btn.btn-action:hover { background: rgba(6,182,199,0.18); }
    .btn.btn-flip {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(139,92,246,0.85), rgba(6,182,199,0.85));
      border-color: transparent;
    }
    .btn.btn-flip.active { outline: 3px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.32); }
    .open-progress {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 380px;
      margin: 6px auto 0;
      height: 4px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .open-progress > span {
      display: block;
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      transition: width 260ms var(--ease);
    }


    /* DOBRA FÍSICA — PAINÉIS CONECTADOS POR VINCOS REAIS */
    .fold-sim {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 3;
      width: min(100%, var(--sim-total-w));
      height: var(--sim-h);
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
      perspective: 2200px;
      overflow: visible;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 30px 34px rgba(0,0,0,0.38));
      animation: none;
    }

    .fold-sim-inner {
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      top: 50%;
      width: var(--sim-total-w);
      height: var(--sim-h);
      transform:
        translate(-50%, -50%)
        rotateX(var(--sim-rx, 0deg))
        rotateY(var(--sim-ry, -6deg));
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
    }

    .fold-sim .page {
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      width: var(--panel-w);
      height: var(--panel-h);
      aspect-ratio: auto;
      border-radius: 0;
      backface-visibility: visible;
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
      transition: none;
      will-change: transform, filter;
    }

    .fold-sim .page::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0 auto 0 0;
      width: 2px;
      z-index: 12;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.24), transparent);
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0.62;
    }

    .fold-sim .page:first-child { border-top-left-radius: 10px; border-bottom-left-radius: 10px; }
    .fold-sim .page:last-child { border-top-right-radius: 10px; border-bottom-right-radius: 10px; }

    .fold-sim .page:not(:first-child) {
      box-shadow:
        inset 1px 0 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.18),
        inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.08),
        0 10px 22px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
    }

    .fold-sim.mode-gate .page::before { opacity: 0.48; }

    .fold-range-wrap {
      width: min(100%, 540px);
      display: grid;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.055);
    }

    .fold-range-label {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.76);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .fold-range-wrap input[type="range"] {
      width: 100%;
      accent-color: var(--accent);
      cursor: ew-resize;
      touch-action: pan-x;
    }

    /* Movimento imediato: a barra não pode ficar lutando contra animações/re-renderizações. */
    .fold-range-wrap .open-progress > span { transition: none; }
    .fold-sim { animation: none; }
    .fold-sim .page { transition: none; }

    .book-wrap {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 3;
      width: min(100%, var(--doc-width));
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 30px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.36));
      animation: flatIn 680ms var(--ease) both;
    }
    .book-wrap.single { grid-template-columns: 1fr; width: min(100%, calc(var(--doc-width) / 2)); }
    .book-wrap .page { aspect-ratio: var(--page-w) / var(--page-h); }
    .book-spine {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0 auto 0 50%;
      z-index: 12;
      width: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.24), transparent);
      transform: translateX(-1px);
    }
    .book-wrap.turning .page:last-child { transform-origin: left center; animation: bookTurn 760ms var(--ease) both; }
    @keyframes bookTurn { from { transform: rotateY(-58deg); filter: brightness(0.78); } to { transform: rotateY(0deg); filter: brightness(1); } }

    .flip-card {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 3;
      width: min(100%, var(--doc-width));
      aspect-ratio: var(--page-w) / var(--page-h);
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
      transition: transform 820ms var(--ease);
      filter: drop-shadow(0 28px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.34));
    }
    .flip-card.show-back { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
    .flip-face {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      backface-visibility: hidden;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: var(--paper);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .flip-face.back { transform: rotateY(180deg); }

    .technical-wrap {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 3;
      width: min(100%, 1180px);
      display: grid;
      gap: 22px;
      animation: flatIn 680ms var(--ease) both;
    }
    .artboard-block {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .artboard-title {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 950;
    }
    .artboard-title span:last-child { color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; }
    .artboard-row {
      display: flex;
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 210px;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 20px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.26));
    }
    .artboard-row .panel-page { flex: var(--panel-flex, 1) 1 0; aspect-ratio: auto; min-height: 210px; }

    .packaging-stage {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 3;
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 530px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      perspective: 1800px;
      cursor: grab;
    }
    .packaging-stage:active { cursor: grabbing; }

    .box-object {
      position: relative;
      width: var(--box-w);
      height: var(--box-h);
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
      transform: rotateX(var(--rx, -13deg)) rotateY(var(--ry, -34deg)) scale(var(--zoom, 1));
      transition: transform 100ms linear;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 34px 38px rgba(0,0,0,0.42));
    }

    .box-object::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      top: 50%;
      width: calc(var(--box-w) * 1.02);
      height: calc(var(--box-h) * 1.02);
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%) translateZ(calc(var(--box-d) * -0.52));
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .box-face {
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      top: 50%;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--paper);
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.16),
        inset 0 22px 34px rgba(255,255,255,0.16);
      backface-visibility: visible;
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
    }

    .box-front,
    .box-back {
      width: var(--box-w);
      height: var(--box-h);
      margin-left: calc(var(--box-w) / -2);
      margin-top: calc(var(--box-h) / -2);
    }

    .box-front {
      transform: translateZ(calc(var(--box-d) / 2));
    }

    .box-back {
      transform: rotateY(180deg) translateZ(calc(var(--box-d) / 2));
    }

    .box-right,
    .box-left {
      width: var(--box-d);
      height: var(--box-h);
      margin-left: calc(var(--box-d) / -2);
      margin-top: calc(var(--box-h) / -2);
    }

    .box-right {
      transform: rotateY(90deg) translateZ(calc(var(--box-w) / 2));
    }

    .box-left {
      transform: rotateY(-90deg) translateZ(calc(var(--box-w) / 2));
    }

    .box-top,
    .box-bottom {
      width: var(--box-w);
      height: var(--box-d);
      margin-left: calc(var(--box-w) / -2);
      margin-top: calc(var(--box-d) / -2);
    }

    .box-top {
      transform: rotateX(90deg) translateZ(calc(var(--box-h) / 2));
    }

    .box-bottom {
      transform: rotateX(-90deg) translateZ(calc(var(--box-h) / 2));
    }

    .milk-roof {
      position: absolute;
      width: var(--box-w);
      height: calc(var(--box-d) * 0.82);
      left: 0;
      top: calc(var(--box-d) * -0.38);
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
    }
    .milk-roof-face {
      position: absolute;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--paper);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.14);
    }
    .milk-roof-front, .milk-roof-back {
      width: var(--box-w);
      height: calc(var(--box-d) * 0.64);
      left: 0;
      top: calc(var(--box-d) * 0.22);
    }
    .milk-roof-front { transform-origin: center bottom; transform: rotateX(44deg) translateZ(calc(var(--box-d) / 2)); }
    .milk-roof-back { transform-origin: center bottom; transform: rotateX(-44deg) rotateY(180deg) translateZ(calc(var(--box-d) / 2)); }
    .milk-ridge {
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      top: 0;
      width: 10px;
      height: calc(var(--box-d) * 0.8);
      transform: translateX(-50%) rotateX(90deg) translateZ(calc(var(--box-h) / 2));
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    }

    .pack-flat {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 3;
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      animation: flatIn 680ms var(--ease) both;
    }
    .pack-row { display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: stretch; gap: 0; filter: drop-shadow(0 22px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.28)); }
    .pack-panel { position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: var(--paper); box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .pack-front, .pack-back { width: 190px; height: 290px; }
    .pack-side { width: 90px; height: 290px; }
    .pack-top, .pack-bottom { width: 190px; height: 90px; margin: 0 auto; }

    .controls {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 0 28px 26px;
    }
    .state-tabs, .tool-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      width: min(100%, 1100px);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.36);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    .btn {
      min-height: 48px;
      padding: 0 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      border-radius: 13px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 170ms ease, background 170ms ease, border-color 170ms ease, box-shadow 170ms ease;
    }
    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.26); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.16); box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(0,0,0,0.18); }
    .btn-primary { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(6,182,199,0.95), rgba(14,165,233,0.84)); border-color: transparent; }
    .btn.active { outline: 3px solid rgba(6,182,199,0.22); background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(6,182,199,1), rgba(139,92,246,0.9)); border-color: transparent; }

    .sidebar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 28px;
      align-self: start;
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      max-height: calc(100vh - 56px);
      overflow: auto;
      padding: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--stroke);
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.15), rgba(255,255,255,0.075));
      box-shadow: 0 22px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
      backdrop-filter: blur(22px);
    }

    .section {
      padding: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.055);
    }
    .section-title {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .step-pill {
      display: inline-grid;
      place-items: center;
      min-width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      margin-right: 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(6,182,199,0.18);
      color: #a7f3ff;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 950;
    }

    .project-cards { display: grid; gap: 10px; }
    .project-card {
      width: 100%;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
      align-items: start;
      gap: 12px;
      min-height: 72px;
      padding: 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      color: #fff;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-align: left;
      transition: transform 170ms ease, background 170ms ease, border-color 170ms ease;
    }
    .project-card:hover, .project-card.active { transform: translateY(-1px); border-color: rgba(6,182,199,0.54); background: rgba(6,182,199,0.12); }
    .card-icon { width: 38px; height: 38px; display: grid; place-items: center; border-radius: 14px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); font-size: 18px; }
    .card-copy strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 950; }
    .card-copy span { display: block; color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.35; }

    .field { display: grid; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .field:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .field label { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; }
    select, input[type="number"], input[type="range"] { width: 100%; }
    select, input[type="number"] {
      min-height: 42px;
      padding: 0 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(8, 12, 24, 0.78);
      color: #fff;
      outline: none;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }
    .two-cols { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; }
    .three-cols { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 10px; }

    .toggle {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 11px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.055);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .toggle input { appearance: none; width: 42px; height: 24px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.16); position: relative; cursor: pointer; transition: background 200ms ease; }
    .toggle input::after { content: ""; position: absolute; top: 3px; left: 3px; width: 18px; height: 18px; border-radius: 50%; background: #fff; transition: transform 200ms var(--ease); }
    .toggle input:checked { background: var(--accent); }
    .toggle input:checked::after { transform: translateX(18px); }

    .upload-drop {
      position: relative;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      min-height: 118px;
      padding: 18px;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.24);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      text-align: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 170ms ease, border-color 170ms ease, transform 170ms ease;
    }
    .upload-drop:hover, .upload-drop.dragging { transform: translateY(-1px); border-color: rgba(6,182,199,0.7); background: rgba(6,182,199,0.11); }
    .upload-drop input { position: absolute; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; }
    .upload-drop strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 950; }
    .upload-drop span { display: block; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.45; }

    .upload-list { display: grid; gap: 9px; margin-top: 12px; }
    .file-label {
      position: relative;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto auto;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 9px;
      padding: 9px;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      border-radius: 15px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.055);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 170ms ease, border-color 170ms ease, transform 170ms ease;
    }
    .file-label:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); border-color: rgba(6,182,199,0.54); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.085); }
    .file-label input { position: absolute; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; }
    .file-number { width: 34px; height: 34px; display: grid; place-items: center; border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: #fff; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 950; }
    .file-text { min-width: 0; }
    .file-text strong, .file-text span { display: block; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; }
    .file-text strong { margin-bottom: 2px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 950; }
    .file-text span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 10px; }
    .mini-btn { width: 30px; height: 30px; display: grid; place-items: center; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius: 10px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: #fff; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 950; cursor: pointer; }
    .file-action { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72); font-size: 10px; font-weight: 950; }

    .review-list { display: grid; gap: 8px; }
    .review-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 9px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 14px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.16); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07); color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.4; }
    .review-dot { width: 9px; height: 9px; flex: 0 0 auto; margin-top: 4px; border-radius: 999px; background: var(--success); box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(52,211,153,0.45); }
    .review-item.warn .review-dot { background: var(--warning); box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(251,191,36,0.45); }
    .review-item.danger .review-dot { background: var(--danger); box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(251,113,133,0.45); }
    .hint { margin: 10px 0 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.45; }

    .presentation .sidebar, .presentation .header, .presentation .caption { display: none; }
    .presentation .shell { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .presentation .main { min-height: calc(100vh - 56px); grid-template-rows: minmax(660px, 1fr) auto; }
    .presentation .stage-wrap { min-height: 74vh; }
    .hidden { display: none !important; }

    @media (max-width: 1200px) {
      .shell { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .sidebar { position: relative; top: auto; max-height: none; }
      .header { flex-direction: column; }
      .project-summary { width: 100%; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 8px; }
      .summary-row, .summary-row + .summary-row { display: grid; border-top: 0; padding: 8px; border-radius: 14px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.055); }
      .summary-row strong { text-align: left; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 740px) {
      .app { padding: 12px; }
      .main, .sidebar { border-radius: 22px; }
      .header { padding: 20px 18px 0; }
      .project-summary { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .stage-wrap { padding: 18px 10px; min-height: 520px; }
      .stage-bg { inset: 12px; }
      .viewer { min-height: 440px; }
      .flat-doc, .book-wrap { width: var(--mobile-doc-width, 760px); max-width: none; }
      .state-tabs, .tool-row { padding: 14px; }
      .btn { width: 100%; }
      .project-card, .file-label { grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; }
      .file-action, .mini-btn { display: none; }
      .three-cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  

    /* THREE.JS REAL 3D VIEWER */
    .three-stage {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 3;
      width: min(100%, 980px);
      height: min(64vh, 620px);
      min-height: 480px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 28px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 18%, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), transparent 32%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(8,13,28,0.98), rgba(16,24,39,0.92));
      box-shadow:
        0 30px 90px rgba(0,0,0,0.36),
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .three-stage canvas {
      display: block;
      width: 100% !important;
      height: 100% !important;
    }

    .three-info {
      position: absolute;
      left: 16px;
      bottom: 16px;
      z-index: 5;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.42);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .three-error {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      height: 100%;
      padding: 28px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.76);
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="app" id="app">
    <div class="shell">
      <section class="main">
        <header class="header">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">Mockup inteligente para designers</div>
            <h1>Veja como vai ficar seu projeto</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Escolha o produto gráfico, envie as artes na ordem lógica e visualize como ele será aprovado, dobrado, folheado ou montado em 3D.</p>
          </div>
          <aside class="project-summary" aria-label="Resumo do projeto">
            <div class="summary-row"><span>Produto</span><strong id="summaryProject">Livreto</strong></div>
            <div class="summary-row"><span>Modelo</span><strong id="summaryModel">Roll-fold</strong></div>
            <div class="summary-row"><span>Status</span><strong id="summaryStatus">0 imagens</strong></div>
          </aside>
        </header>

        <section class="stage-wrap">
          <div class="stage-bg"></div>
          <div class="viewer" id="viewer"></div>
          <div class="caption" id="caption">Escolha um tipo de produto e envie suas imagens para começar.</div>
        </section>

        <section class="controls">
          <div class="state-tabs" id="stateTabs"></div>
          <div class="tool-row">
            <button class="btn" id="toggleTitles" type="button">Ocultar títulos</button>
            <button class="btn" id="toggleImages" type="button">Ocultar imagens</button>
            <button class="btn" id="presentationBtn" type="button">Modo apresentação</button>
            <button class="btn" id="resetCameraBtn" type="button">Resetar câmera</button>
          </div>
        </section>
      </section>

      <aside class="sidebar">
        <section class="section">
          <h2 class="section-title"><span><span class="step-pill">1</span>Tipo de produto</span></h2>
          <div class="project-cards" id="productCards">
            <button class="project-card" data-product="book" type="button">
              <span class="card-icon">📖</span>
              <span class="card-copy"><strong>Livro</strong><span>Capa, miolo, virada de páginas e contracapa.</span></span>
            </button>
            <button class="project-card active" data-product="folder" type="button">
              <span class="card-icon">📄</span>
              <span class="card-copy"><strong>Livreto / Folder</strong><span>Bi-fold, roll-fold, sanfona e modo técnico de imposição.</span></span>
            </button>
            <button class="project-card" data-product="frontBack" type="button">
              <span class="card-icon">↔</span>
              <span class="card-copy"><strong>Frente e verso</strong><span>Cartão, flyer simples, tag, postal ou voucher.</span></span>
            </button>
            <button class="project-card" data-product="packaging" type="button">
              <span class="card-icon">◼</span>
              <span class="card-copy"><strong>Embalagem 3D</strong><span>Caixa com largura, altura, profundidade e faces reais.</span></span>
            </button>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <h2 class="section-title"><span><span class="step-pill">2</span>Configuração</span></h2>

          <div class="field" id="folderModelField">
            <label for="foldModel">Tipo de dobra · quantidade de dobras</label>
            <select id="foldModel">
              <optgroup label="1 dobra · 4 páginas">
                <option value="bifold">Bi-fold (meia dobra)</option>
              </optgroup>
              <optgroup label="2 dobras · 6 páginas">
                <option value="rollfold" selected>Roll-fold / Carteira</option>
                <option value="zfold">Z-fold / Sanfona</option>
                <option value="gatefold">Gate-fold / Porta</option>
              </optgroup>
              <optgroup label="3 dobras · 8 páginas">
                <option value="rollfold8">Roll-fold (8 págs)</option>
                <option value="zfold8">Z-fold / Sanfona (8 págs)</option>
                <option value="doubleparallel">Paralela dupla</option>
              </optgroup>
              <optgroup label="4 dobras · 10 páginas">
                <option value="zfold10">Sanfona (10 págs)</option>
                <option value="rollfold10">Roll-fold (10 págs)</option>
              </optgroup>
            </select>
            <p class="hint" style="margin-top:8px;">Cada opção define automaticamente a quantidade de páginas e a imposição (prancha externa/interna).</p>
          </div>

          <div class="field" id="pageCountField">
            <label for="pageCount">Número de páginas</label>
            <select id="pageCount">
              <option value="2">2 páginas</option>
              <option value="4">4 páginas</option>
              <option value="6" selected>6 páginas</option>
              <option value="8">8 páginas</option>
              <option value="10">10 páginas</option>
              <option value="12">12 páginas</option>
              <option value="16">16 páginas</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="field" id="ratioField">
            <label for="ratioPreset">Formato das páginas</label>
            <select id="ratioPreset">
              <option value="iso" selected>A4 — padrão</option>
              <option value="custom">Personalizada</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="two-cols hidden" id="customRatioFields">
            <div class="field"><label for="customW">Largura</label><input id="customW" type="number" min="0.1" step="0.01" value="1"></div>
            <div class="field"><label for="customH">Altura</label><input id="customH" type="number" min="0.1" step="0.01" value="1.414"></div>
          </div>

          <div id="foldTechnicalFields">
            <label class="toggle">
              <span>Modo técnico de imposição</span>
              <input id="technicalMode" type="checkbox">
            </label>
            <div id="compensationField" class="hidden">
              <input id="compensationMm" type="hidden" value="0">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div id="packagingFields" class="hidden">
            <div class="field">
              <label for="packageType">Tipo de embalagem</label>
              <select id="packageType">
                <option value="carton">Cartucho vertical</option>
                <option value="milk">Caixa de leite / longa vida</option>
                <option value="box">Caixa comum de papelão</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="three-cols">
              <div class="field"><label for="boxWidth">Largura</label><input id="boxWidth" type="number" min="20" step="1" value="90"></div>
              <div class="field"><label for="boxHeight">Altura</label><input id="boxHeight" type="number" min="20" step="1" value="160"></div>
              <div class="field"><label for="boxDepth">Profundidade</label><input id="boxDepth" type="number" min="10" step="1" value="55"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label for="zoomRange">Zoom do mockup 3D</label>
              <input id="zoomRange" type="range" min="0.55" max="1.55" step="0.01" value="1">
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <h2 class="section-title"><span><span class="step-pill">3</span>Upload</span></h2>
          <label class="upload-drop" id="bulkDrop">
            <input id="bulkUpload" type="file" accept="image/*" multiple>
            <span><strong>Enviar várias imagens</strong><span>Distribuição automática na ordem lógica: imagem 1 → Página 1, imagem 2 → Página 2...</span></span>
          </label>
          <div class="upload-list" id="uploadList"></div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <h2 class="section-title"><span><span class="step-pill">4</span>Revisão inteligente</span></h2>
          <div class="review-list" id="reviewList"></div>
          <p class="hint">A revisão ajuda a evitar ordem errada, proporções incompatíveis e baixa resolução antes de apresentar ao cliente.</p>
        </section>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/three.js/r128/three.min.js"></script>
  <script>
    const RATIO_PRESETS = {
